    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udcbc $34,000 - A dependable, well-kept ride that delivers real value! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it's been thoughtfully maintained and shows only the minor cosmetic wear you'd expect from a car that's actually been enjoyed. Mechanically sound and ready for the road, it strikes a great balance between quality and affordability. If you're looking for a reliable daily driver without the mint-condition price tag, this one deserves a serious look!",
