    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project car or a no-frills runner? This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it starts and moves under its own power, which is a great starting point for the right buyer! It does come with noticeable wear, cosmetic issues, and will need some meaningful attention to get it into better shape. If you're handy with repairs or looking for a budget entry into ownership, this could be your opportunity \u2014 priced accordingly to reflect its current state!",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 A reliable, well-maintained vehicle at a great price \u2014 this car is in genuinely good condition and ready for its next adventure! The exterior looks sharp with only the minor scuffs and blemishes you'd expect from normal everyday use, and the interior is clean and comfortable with light wear that shows it's been lived in but well cared for. Mechanically, it runs and drives great \u2014 this is a car you can feel confident buying. If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle without the mint-condition price tag, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition \u2014 a project car or parts vehicle that requires significant attention before it can be considered reliable transportation. The exterior shows considerable wear, including rust, dents, and faded or peeling paint across multiple panels. The interior is worn and damaged, with torn upholstery, broken trim pieces, and non-functional components. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require substantial repair work \u2014 it is not currently in a state suitable for daily driving. This listing is best suited for experienced mechanics, hobbyists looking for a restoration project, or buyers seeking a parts source. Please be prepared for a significant investment of time and money beyond the purchase price. Sold as-is with no warranty implied.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you about what you're getting. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 the paint is faded, chipped, and scratched in multiple areas, and there is visible rust on the body panels and undercarriage that will require attention. The interior is worn throughout, with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and a dashboard that shows its age. Mechanically, the car has known issues: it runs, but it is not reliable for daily driving without repairs \u2014 expect to invest in work on the engine, suspension, and possibly the transmission. This is best suited for a buyer who is handy with repairs, looking for a project vehicle, or needs parts. We are pricing it accordingly and encourage you to inspect it thoroughly before purchase.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 a designation we reserve exclusively for cars that truly earn it, and this one does so without reservation. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint retains a deep, uniform gloss with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and every body panel sits with factory-correct alignment. The interior is equally impressive, with seats, carpets, and trim all looking and feeling fresh \u2014 no fading, cracking, or wear of any kind. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with all components functioning exactly as intended. This is a car that has clearly been cared for meticulously throughout its life, and a prospective buyer can step in with full confidence that they are getting a vehicle at the very top of its game.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    }
